headline: Is Intuitive Surgical (ISRG) Still Priced For Perfection After Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: If you are wondering whether Intuitive Surgical is fairly priced at around US$495 per share, you are not alone. Many investors are asking whether the current level still makes sense. The stock has recently shown a mixed pattern, with a 3.4% return over the last 7 days, a 15.5% decline over the last 30 days, and returns of an 11.9% decline year to date and a 16.3% decline over the last year, while still showing a 105.4% return over 3 years and an 87.6% return over 5 years. headline: Should You Buy ISRG Stock Despite a 13% Fall in Three Months?
summary: ISRG has lost 13% in three months, but strong da Vinci 5 adoption and rising procedures raise a bigger question: is this pullback a buying opportunity?
